commit 584990a347367c0d63c5b831cceee579c8568911
Author: Iwao AVE! <harawata@gmail.com>
Date:   Sat Dec 17 12:07:35 2022 +0900

    When processing DynamicSqlSource, evaluate param values in scripting phase

    - Evaluated param values are stored in `ParameterMapping` and later used in DefaultParameterHandler
    - There is no change when processing RawSqlSource
    - Removed unused `injectionFilter` from TextSqlNode (gh-117)

    This should fix #2754 .

    This might also fix #206 and #575 , but with this patch, it still is not possible to invoke a method with parameter inside a parameter reference like `#{_parameter.mymethod(_parameter.value)}`.
    It might be possible to accept OGNL expression in a param reference (e.g. `#{${_parameter.mymethod(_parameter.value)}}`), but I'm not sure if that's a good idea.

